---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Our Process – Utah Oasis Homes">
  <section class="section">
    <div class="section-header">
      <h1 class="section-title">Our Process</h1>
      <p class="section-subtitle">
        A clear, guided path from first conversation to your finished home.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="card-grid">
      <article class="card">
        <h2>01 — Discover</h2>
        <p>
          We begin with a detailed conversation about your lifestyle, priorities, budget, and land.
          This is where we listen more than we talk.
        </p>
      </article>
      <article class="card">
        <h2>02 — Design</h2>
        <p>
          Working with trusted design partners, we shape a home that captures your vision while
          maximizing your site, light, and views.
        </p>
      </article>
      <article class="card">
        <h2>03 — Build</h2>
        <p>
          Once construction begins, you receive regular updates, clear timelines, and on-site walk-
          throughs so you always know what’s next.
        </p>
      </article>
      <article class="card">
        <h2>04 — Live</h2>
        <p>
          We finish with a careful handover, walk-through, and support as you settle into a home
          designed to feel like an everyday retreat.
        </p>
      </article>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
